Network library and associated test programs in C++20.

This project has been tested on the following platforms:

+===========+=====================+====================+========+========+
| OS Family | Distribution        | OS Version (Port)  | GCC    | Clang  |
+===========+=====================+====================+========+========+
| GNU/Linux | Debian              | 11 (amd64)         | 10.2.1 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | Fedora              | 35 (x86_64)        | 11.2.1 | 13.0.0 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE Leap       | 15.3 (x86_64)      | 11.2.1 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE Tumbleweed | 20220530 (x86_64)  | 12.1.0 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | Red Hat (RHEL)      | 8.5 (x86_64)       | 11.2.1 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------+--------+--------+
